	(1776, 'These tunnels that you see are called timeways. They are infinite in number. The ones that currently exist in your reality are what the master has deemed as \'trouble spots.\'  These trouble spots may differ completely in theme but they always share a cause. That is, their existence is a result of the same temporal disturbance. Remember that should you venture inside one...\n', 20129, 7, 15, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 17661),
