	(2434, 'You don\'t remember me? When you were a child your mother would leave you in my care while she served at the Temple of the Moon. I held you in my arms and fed you honey and sheep\'s milk to calm you until she would return. You were my little angel. Blasted Scourge... What have they done to you, $n?', 29061, 23, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 29326),
