	(5942, 'Attention!', 25162, 14, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 26245),
	(5943, 'Hello to you new recruits. I\'m Drill Sergeant Bahduum. For the next few days, you\'re going to receive orientation.', 25162, 15, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 24195),
	(5944, 'The Isle of Quel\'Danas has been overrun by the forces of Prince Kael\'thas Sunstrider. Intel had him pegged as deceased. Intel was wrong.', 25162, 16, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 24196),
	(5945, 'Up on the plateau, he and his demon friends are trying to reignite the Sunwell and open a rift to bring their head-honcho, Kil\'Jaeden, back into the world.', 25162, 17, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 24197),
	(5946, 'Our job is to clear out as much of his fodder as we can, while supporting the specialists that the powers-that-be are having brought in.', 25162, 18, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 24198),
