	(10695, 'No gnome will be left behind.', 6221, 4, 12, 7, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10696, 'Success! Huzzah! The power source restored the necklace!', 6826, 4, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10697, 'We\'re almost to safety. From here, we run. Try not to get too far behind! GO!', 8284, 4, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10698, 'This is it, $N. My stuff should be in that room. Cover me, I\'m going in!', 9023, 4, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10699, 'That one\'s empty!!', 9503, 4, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10700, 'Open it. We need to hurry up. I can smell those Dark Irons coming a mile away and I can tell you one thing, they\'re COMING!', 9682, 4, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10701, 'Majesty, run while you still can. She is not what you think her to be...', 12580, 4, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10702, 'Dying... See the light... gloriouss...', 12936, 4, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10703, 'Goodbye, cruel world... I\'m leavin\' you today... goodbye... goodbye... goodbye...', 12938, 4, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10704, 'My scepter will once again become whole!', 13716, 4, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10705, 'I say we fire it. Cut the rope.', 16580, 4, 12, 1, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10706, 'You know too much!', 16769, 5, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10707, 'Sid! Ale, NOW!', 16821, 4, 12, 7, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10708, 'SIR! YES, SIR! Reporting for duty, sir!', 16864, 4, 12, 7, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10709, 'Take care of him, Sid. He may be the only link I have to my father and mother. He needs to sober up...', 16886, 4, 12, 7, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10710, 'Do you hear something?', 16993, 6, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10711, 'We will never be without power! I have secured our future! Bask in my glory!', 17008, 4, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10712, 'Hrm, this looks much better. Let\'s have a look on the inside.', 17222, 4, 12, 7, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10713, 'It\'s ironic, I hate the ocean but I love the beach.', 17243, 8, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10714, 'Cursed scum!', 17819, 4, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10715, 'Blackmoore will have... your head!', 17833, 4, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10716, 'That\'ll do it! Quickly, take cover!', 17982, 4, 12, 7, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10717, 'I wanna be just like the pitfighter!', 18293, 4, 12, 1, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10718, 'Eat me already! I can\'t take being locked up in this cage around you stinky, fat slobs.', 18369, 4, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10719, 'We have done it! Thrall would be proud.', 18384, 4, 12, 1, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10720, 'For shure it be good.', 18396, 4, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10721, 'My children will be made orphans!', 18428, 8, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10722, 'In time, you may learn to see through their deceptions.', 18537, 4, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10723, 'Affiliation: Burning Legion', 18896, 4, 12, 7, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10724, 'The water spirits are perhaps the most outspoken. They are generous and understanding. Indeed, if you are having trouble hearing the voices, it is with water that you should begin.', 18917, 4, 12, 7, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10725, 'Your efforts... are in vain.', 18994, 4, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10726, 'Dangerous out there, innit? Know what ya need? Protection. I can help ya defy death itself! Ya wear this madstone \'round yer neck, see, and then ya be able to come back if ya find yerself in the spirit world! Just a quick jaunt to yer corpse and up ya com', 19227, 9, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10727, 'Thank you for speaking to the men, Almonen. They\'ll be better for it.', 19272, 4, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10728, 'Listen up, soldiers!', 19346, 6, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10729, 'As you command, sir.', 19377, 4, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10730, 'You DO know that marksmen are issued blanks for practice drills, right?', 19475, 5, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10731, 'Hmm, arcane annihilators are pretty tough. I wonder if Papa Wheeler knows what he\'s asking for?', 19541, 5, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10732, 'Fascinating.', 19612, 4, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10733, 'Come on! Clear!', 19623, 4, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10734, 'Chubis Chubisimo! Get those things fixed... we haven\'t got all day!', 19645, 4, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10735, 'Get \'em hot and fresh while you can. You won\'t find a better price on muffins anywhere else in Shattrath.', 19664, 6, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10736, 'No word from the nexus-prince as of yet. Rumors of a dispute with our clients in Netherstorm have begun to circulate. Our Sodaraami backers speak of divesting. We\'ve dispatched our top negotiators to dissuade them, sir.', 19667, 4, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10737, 'Looking at these energy levels, Shaffar was set to make a killing!', 19671, 4, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10738, 'Why don\'t you pick up a hammer and start banging on these structures instead of asking us if it\'s done every 5 minutes?', 19672, 4, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10739, 'Here goes nothing!', 19673, 4, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10740, 'Well, it\'s like I said; it\'s going to be a while before we get this ship ready for flight. We\'ll keep you informed.', 19737, 4, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10741, 'Oh no, no, no... I\'m a rocket man.', 19776, 4, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10742, 'You do recall the last time that this occurred, yes? Let us hope that the master need not be involved.', 19932, 4, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10743, 'Culuthas, when I find you, I am going to make certain that you suffer for all eternity!', 20133, 4, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10744, 'We must stand at the ready. I have faced undead before. They are ruthless killing machines, devoid of any emotion or compassion.', 20345, 4, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10745, 'It\'s not him I\'m worried about. It\'s these new rookies around here - and those creepy purple elves they brought with \'em. They ain\'t even proved themselves yet.\r\n', 20513, 4, 12, 7, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10746, 'I hate flesh beasts...', 20603, 4, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10747, 'Taste pure energy!', 20727, 4, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10748, 'Kael\'thas and the Legion... just what we needed!', 20780, 4, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10749, 'Alright, keep me protected while I plant this disruptor. This shouldn\'t take very long.', 20802, 4, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10750, 'The... The fire lord? An elemental lord was unearthed? Of course... Gul\'dan you were a damned fool!', 21024, 4, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10751, 'They have abandoned us! Do not forget!', 21049, 4, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10752, 'You will not save him!', 21137, 4, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10753, 'If my blood hadn\'t clotted long ago, it would be boiling with rage right now...', 21279, 4, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10754, 'The Legion reigns!', 21661, 5, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10755, 'Hello.', 22423, 4, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10756, 'The Light is my guide... it is my sustenance!', 22431, 4, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10757, 'I see you ancestors, Anchorite! They writhe and scream in the darkness... they are with us!', 22432, 4, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10758, 'I\'ve got five kids, man! They\'ll die without me!', 28557, 9, 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0);
